8 Slowly open the door and peer into the room
9 Kick the door as hard as you can and run through
10 Timmidly knock on the door, wondering who might answer

You jump from the bed as quickly and quietly as you can and fumble in the dark as you attempt to run towards the direction of the light. As you get closer to the light source it becomes obvious to you that it might be a way out. Finally, after what feels like an eternity you reach the light at the edge of the room and wait. You can see that the door opens into the next room. All you hear now is an eerie silence. 
What do you do next?
